'''阿尔派歐洲區域方程式錦標賽'''（{{lang-en|Formula Regional European Championship by Alpine}}）是[[国际汽车联合会|国际汽车联合会]]批准的區域性統一規格賽車的[[三級方程式賽車|三級方程式賽車]]級別賽事。該錦標賽於2019年開始舉辦，由{{le|意大利汽車俱樂部|Automobile Club d'Italia}}和WSK卡丁車推廣合作舉辦。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Wood |first1=Elliot |title=Italian bid beats Renault to run European regional F3 series |url=http://www.formulascout.com/italian-bid-beats-renault-to-run-european-regional-f3-series/45704 |accessdate=2 November 2018 |work=formulascout.com |publisher=Formula Scout |date=12 October 2018 |archive-date=2021-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117164713/https://formulascout.com/italian-bid-beats-renault-to-run-european-regional-f3-series/45704 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

首屆錦標賽將在歐洲巡迴賽上進行八輪比賽，其中一半在意大利舉行。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Allen |first1=Peter |title=Prema commits to Italian-promoted European Regional F3 championship |url=http://www.formulascout.com/prema-commits-to-italian-promoted-european-regional-f3-series/46127 |accessdate=2 November 2018 |work=formulascout.com |publisher=Formula Scout |date=2 November 2018 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108132622/https://formulascout.com/prema-commits-to-italian-promoted-european-regional-f3-series/46127 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 總成績前九名的車手將獲得[[FIA超級駕駛執照|FIA超級駕駛執照]]積分。

由2021年賽季開始，[[雷諾方程式2.0歐洲盃|雷諾方程式歐洲盃]]將會與歐洲區域方程式錦標賽合併，成為阿尔派歐洲區域方程式錦標賽。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Smith |first1=Luke |title=Formula Regional Europe merges with Renault Eurocup for 2021 |url=https://www.motorsport.com/frenault/news/formula-regional-european-merger-2021/4901832/?ic_source=home-page-widget&ic_medium=widget&ic_campaign=widget-22 |accessdate=31 October 2020 |work=Motorsport.com |publisher=Motorsport.com |date=31 October 2020 |archive-date=2021-10-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211021135643/https://www.motorsport.com/frenault/news/formula-regional-european-merger-2021/4901832/?ic_source=home-page-widget&ic_medium=widget&ic_campaign=widget-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

